13:28.040 --> 13:28.770
Cepat pergi.

13:30.840 --> 13:31.840
Perlahan-lahan.

13:32.240 --> 13:33.240
Perlahan-lahan.

13:36.360 --> 13:37.640
Cepatlah pergi!

13:38.280 --> 13:40.280
