13:40.800 --> 13:41.640
Panggillah!

13:41.880 --> 13:44.410
Saya panggil sahaja, tapi mereka tak datang.

13:44.960 --> 13:45.760
Tuan.

13:46.960 --> 13:47.800
Puan.

13:49.160 --> 13:50.240
Perlahan-lahan.

14:05.920 --> 14:06.680
Cepat pergi.

14:12.360 --> 14:14.160
Tuan, mari duduk sekejap.

14:16.920 --> 14:17.280
Tuan.

14:17.280 --> 14:17.800
Ayah.

14:17.840 --> 14:18.960
Hati-hati.

14:36.560 --> 14:37.280
Beca, beca.

14:37.400 --> 14:38.800
Jalan, jalan, jalan. Ke jeti, ke jeti.

14:38.800 --> 14:40.040
Tak tarik lagi, tak tarik lagi.

14:40.040 --> 14:41.280
Bukan macam tu, abang. Tolonglah.

14:41.280 --> 14:42.940
Isteri saya dah nak bersalin.

14:43.160 --> 14:44.400
Saya nak cepat jemput orang.

14:44.400 --> 14:45.160
Macam inilah.

14:45.160 --> 14:46.760
